# InfiniSynapse Core Rules

- Read `AGENTS.md` before changing InfiniSynapse integration code.
- Search `upstream-docs/infinisynapse-site/zh/markdown/` before using an endpoint; English docs are supplemental only.
- Keep API Key server-side.
- Connect `GET /api/ai/events?connId=` before `POST /api/ai/message`.
- Use workspace APIs for deliverables: `getTaskWorkspace`, `previewFile`, `downloadTaskFile`.
- For private deployment, check `AUTHING_SERVER_URL` first.
